42 (c) On and after January 1, 2026, no multipurpose off-highway vehicle shall be returned
43 for or subject to ad valorem taxation. The procedures prescribed in this chapter for
44 returning tangible personal property for ad valorem taxation and collecting the ad valorem
45 taxes imposed on tangible personal property shall not apply to any multipurpose
46 off-highway vehicle."
47 SECTION 3.
48 This Act shall become effective on January 1, 2026, and shall be applicable to taxable years
49 beginning on or after January 1, 2026.
50 SECTION 4.
51 All laws and parts of laws in conflict with this Act are repealed.
